descriptionHtml:
That is (ultra armor)
new version (ultra armor 1.1)
CBBEv3_1 female armor of three colors
gold silver and roman.
Each of these arms is composed of 25 parts
the man can attract simultaneously.
All parts are enchanted
each part has 10 Enchantment to 100%
the strength is on Daedric Armor.
All parts are manufactured in the smithyand with console,example " Help gold  "
"   player.additem id  1   ".
you can combine all three color.
you can put all the parts or take off.
you can give your companion the full armor.
you have dwemer Armor 4 parts
 1 Cuirass 2 Boots 3 Gauntlets 4 cycled
 Reason is quest returned the lexicon
 if you have Ancient Knowledge
 then you have 25% rates to your Armor.
you are dovahkiin
you are strongly slightly fast.
you are immune against effects in magic, poisons, diseases and vampirism.
You can carry a lot of weight and remains fast and light.
you can swim under water without drowning.
and much more.
